     <h2>
      <a href="/">
       mnmlst
      </a>
      :
      <b>
       th lst fr nw thngs
      </b>
     </h2>
     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       A cpl dys g I wrt bt
       <a href="http://mnmlist.com/7-ways-to-avoid-buying-new-stuff/">
        ltrntvs t byng nw thngs
       </a>
       , nd smn rpld n Twttr:
      </p>
      <p>
       “I wnt t hv th mny t by nw thngs!”
      </p>
      <p>
       Or smthng lk tht (I’m t lzy t g bck nd fnd th twt). Ths chs  prtty cmmn sntmnt: mny ppl dn’t wnt t b frgl, t cnsrv, t b mnmlst … thy wnt t by nw thngs.
      </p>
      <p>
       Evn ths f s wh try t b mnmlsts hv ths rgs — whn Appl nnncd ts nw prdcts ystrdy, fr xmpl, I spnt mst f th dy drlng, lstng ftr th lrg-scrnd Mc nd th nw wrlss ms. My pls ctlly rss nd I gt  rsh f drnln whn I thnk bt ths nw Appl prdcts (vn nw, s I rflct n t, t’s hppnng).
      </p>
      <p>
       Ths lst s nt nq t Appl fnbs lk m — w ll fl t. W’r ll sscptbl t dvrtsng — sm ppl lst vr nw shs, nw clths, nw gdgts, nw pwr tls, nw crs, nw hms, nw bks, nw grmt fd, nd s n. W ll hv r wknsss, r lst trggrs.
      </p>
      <p>
       Th ky s t b wr f t. Ntc th xctmnt, th rsd hrtbt, th shllw brthng, th drnln rsh tht cms wth th lst vr  prdct. Ntc th symptms r vry mch lk sxl rsl? It’s prctclly th sm — nd jst lk whn w’r sxlly rsd, th rtnl prt f r brns sht dwn. Ths shttng dwn s why w mk stpd sxl dcsns (why I hv sx kds, fr xmpl) vn thgh w knw bttr whn w’r nt rsd.
      </p>
      <p>
       S f w cn’t thnk rtnlly whn w’r rsd fr nw stff, wht shld w d?
      </p>
      <p>
       A fw thngs:
       <span id="more-448">
       </span>
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        1. Avd dvrtsng
       </strong>
       . Tht mns sht ff th cbl
       <span class="caps">
        TV,
       </span>
       nd thr vd tlvsn r wtch v d-fr Tv r Appl TV r smthng lk tht. It mns stp rdng d-flld mgzns nd blgs, nd fcs n ths tht prvd vl wtht ll th ds (r s d-blckrs n th Intrnt).
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        2. Avd shppng
       </strong>
       . It’s hrd t vd th lst whn w’r n  mll r Wllmrt r sm trndy str tht hs btfl lstfl stff (.. th Appl Str fr m). S dn’t g t ths plcs f y cn vd t. Only g whn bsltly ncssry, knw xctly wht y’r gng t by nd nly by tht.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        3. Whn y d gt th lst, b cnscs f t
       </strong>
       . Tk sm dp brths. Wlk t ff. Thnk bt rtnl thngs, t ngg yr rtnl brn. Fr xmpl, sk yrslf qstns: “D I rlly nd ths? Cn I d wtht t? Wll I rgrt ths ltr?”
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        4. Rcgnz rtnlzng
       </strong>
       . Thr’s  dffrnc btwn rtnl thnkng nd rtnlzng. Or brns r gd t rtnlzng: “Ths wll ctlly sv m mny. Ths s ncssry fr my bsnss. I dsrv  trt nw nd thn. I’m svng mny f I by tw. Lk hw prtty!” Ntc ths thnkng, nd rcgnz t fr wht t s. And stp yrslf whn y d t.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        5. Ps
       </strong>
       . Y dn’t nd t by rght wy. Wt  dy r tw. Or  wk. D y nd t rght ths scnd? Uslly th nswr s n. S wt, nd wt, nd wt sm mr. I’v sggstd th 30-dy lst. I sd ths mthd whn I bght my bk rcntly — I ctlly wtd mr thn 6 mnths bfr byng t, bcs I wntd t b sr ths ws  rl nd.
      </p>
      <p>
       S I’m nt gng t by  nw Mc, gt  nw ms, r gt th 17-nch Mcbk Pr I’v bn drlng vr fr sm tm. I lrdy hv  grt Mc nd  grt Mcbk Ar (whch I’m typng n rght nw). I cn wt ntl nxt yr r ltr t gt  nw mchn, bcs wht I hv rght nw s gd ngh. Bttr thn gd ngh.
      </p>
      <p>
       If wht y lrdy hv s gd ngh, why pgrd? Why gv n t th lst? Rcgnz tht y’r lrdy hppy, tht dvrtsng hs crtd ths dsr n y, nd tht y cn b cntnt wtht t.
      </p>
      <p>
       <small>
       </small>
      </p>
